node.text: I can’t believe it was 4 years ago today that I launched Uncommon James out of a room in my house. It’s incredible what we’ve done in those 4 short years- I sometimes still can’t believe it’s real. Thankful for everyone’s support...it’s because of you guys that I’m able to live a dream...and I will never forget that. Here’s a look back at the very first video we ever shot at our first campaign shoot. Feels like yesterday ♥️

node.text: It was clearly a good time doing the wine tasting to pick my favorite 3 red wines for my Cavallari Collection box with @dryfarmwines …my box is available for 30 days and I can’t wait for you all the try them. The 3 I landed on are perfect for date night, a picnic, and self care night (think bath or curled up reading a book). If you’ve been following me for a minute, then you know I love Dry Farm Wine bc it’s organic, low in sugar and sulfites, they care about the soil health, and it’s honestly the only wine I can drink that doesn’t give me a headache. Not that I’ve tried it, but even after multiple bottles still no hangover 😜. This partnership started bc I’m a legit fan…and I’m honored to have my own box. So check it out! DryFarmWines.com/CavallariCollection
